article_title: The 25 Best Fast Food Restaurants in 2016
article_text:
25. Penn Station East Coast Subs*

This chain has the highest rankings in a recent industry survey among sub joints in the categories of food quality, likely to recommend and likely to return.

*Rankings and data from Nation’s Restaurant News.
